@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ejhreg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.30 * v2 + 0.59) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.13)) + 0.90)
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.75 * v0 + 0.28)) * 0.54)
    data[tid] = v0
